# Quick Dinner

#  Ingredients:
#  3 favorite fruits
#  (frozen or fresh)
#  8oz plain greek yogurt
#  1 cup raw leafy green veggie
#  8 oz water
#  1/2 cup ice (optional)
#  1-2 peanut butter bars


#  Directions:

#  Put water, yogurt, green veggie, and fruit 
#  into blender, vitamix or nutribullet.  Blend
#  until smooth.  If desired, add ice and blend
#  again until smooth.  Pour into cup, drink 
#  and enjoy.  Cut open peanut butter bar and 
#  enjoy.
